"roleForDisplay\":\"editor\",\"name\":\"DreUpdate\",\"login\":\"DreUpdate\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isMemeVerified\":false,\"iq\":250383,\"id\":2457824,\"humanReadableRoleForDisplay\":\"Editor\",\"headerImageUrl\":\"https://images.genius.com/f96c073b0bd60c3917b2adbea110f7df.1000x563x1.jpg\",\"avatar\":{\"medium\":{\"boundingBox\":{\"height\":400,\"width\":300},\"url\":\"https://images.genius.com/avatars/medium/462a2b75c4f2f4fee92f24f495feafcb\"},\"small\":{\"boundingBox\":{\"height\":100,\"width\":100},\"url\":\"https://images.genius.com/avatars/small/462a2b75c4f2f4fee92f24f495feafcb\"},\"thumb\":{\"boundingBox\":{\"height\":32,\"width\":32},\"url\":\"https://images.genius.com/avatars/thumb/462a2b75c4f2f4fee92f24f495feafcb\"},\"tiny\":{\"boundingBox\":{\"height\":16,\"width\":16},\"url\":\"https://images.genius.com/avatars/tiny/462a2b75c4f2f4fee92f24f495feafcb\"}},\"apiPath\":\"/users/2457824\",\"aboutMeSummary\":\"Spanish/English\\n\\n\\nCurrent Projects\\n•musicals & Disney\\n•\\\"The Music Man\\\" / “Oklahoma” / “The King and I” / “Grease”\\n\\nMentions & Achievements\\n•#1 on the All-time Leaderboard for Lullaby. Disney & Children’s Music\\n•#2 on the All-Time Leaderboard for, Musicals & Broadway\\n\\n•Top Scholars Weekly #122, #123, #125, #127, #137, #139, #140, #141, #142, #144, #145, #146, #148, #149\\n\\n•August, September, October monthly clean-up championships (2020)\\n\\n  \\n\\n\\nMy Genius Journey\\n\\n\\n\\nI initially created a Genius account in 2014 when I was in middle school, but I really only used it to look at lyrics and maybe upvote annotations.\\n\\nI didn’t really become a contributor to the site until April 2020 because of being in quarantine. I started spending a lot of time on here and gained IQ pretty fast, mainly by working meta/transcriptions for Disney and children’s music, which is where over half of my IQ is from.\\n\\nAround June, I began posting in the forums more and participated in the Pride Month Spotlight. Then, in August I participated in and won my first clean-up championship and hit 50,000 IQ. I went on to win the September and October championships as well.\\n\\nIn September, I designed a new cover art for and became a co-host to the Get Involved! community series with ed Scopey, posting biweekly prompts for the Genius community to share about themselves. I also wrote my most upvoted annotation to date about some fun wordplay on Kendrick Lamar’s Pulitzer Prize win for “Friday Night Cypher.”\\n\\nIn October I hit 100,000 IQ! In November for the 2020 Genius Awards, I was voted the Best Contributor, as well as second-place for the Rookie of the Year and Most Creative User.\\n\\nSince then, I’ve been spending less time on Genius to focus on school, but when I’m here I’m usually transcribing and cleaning up musicals, especially oldies.\\n\\n*yes that’s me in my pfp\",\"type\":\"user\"},\"2976672\":{\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"interactions\":{\"following\":false},\"excludedPermissions\":[\"follow\"],\"permissions\":[]},\"url\":\"https://genius.com/Gary\",\"roleForDisplay\":\"staff\",\"name\":\"Gary\",\"login\":\"Gary\",\"isVerified\":false,\"isMemeVerified\":false,\"iq\":444409,\"id\":2976672,\"humanReadableRoleForDisplay\":\"Staff\",\"headerImageUrl\":\"https://filepicker-images.genius.com/l1pegbzlvms\",\"avatar\":{\"medium\":{\"boundingBox\":{\"height\":400,\"width\":300},\"url\":\"https://images.genius.com/avatars/medium/cc8cb9cfb7d0483ceb806db951b86733\"},\"small\":{\"boundingBox\":{\"height\":100,\"width\":100},\"url\":\"https://images.genius.com/avatars/small/cc8cb9cfb7d0483ceb806db951b86733\"},\"thumb\":{\"boundingBox\":{\"height\":32,\"width\":32},\"url\":\"https://images.genius.com/avatars/thumb/cc8cb9cfb7d0483ceb806db951b86733\"},\"tiny\":{\"boundingBox\":{\"height\":16,\"width\":16},\"url\":\"https://images.genius.com/avatars/tiny/cc8cb9cfb7d0483ceb806db951b86733\"}},\"apiPath\":\"/users/2976672\",\"aboutMeSummary\":\"\",\"type\":\"user\"},\"3499648\":{\"currentUserMetadata\":{\"int